# IBMS / UFMS Boundary Guard

IBMS and UFMS are separate systems. In this repository, default scope is IBMS only.

If any UFMS-specific path, code, menu, API, schema, seed, migration, auth logic, deployment logic, or documentation is detected during an IBMS task, stop immediately and report to the user.

Do not copy UFMS source into IBMS.
Do not copy IBMS source into UFMS.
Do not merge UFMS backend/frontend/prisma/database/auth/menu/seed logic into IBMS unless the user explicitly approves that exact cross-system operation.

Allowed cross-system work is limited to explicit API contracts, data mapping documents, and integration specifications.

Before every task:
1. confirm current repository path
2. confirm task scope is IBMS
3. check for UFMS boundary risk
4. stop if boundary risk exists
